headline: KLA Corporation (KLAC): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Over the past six months, KLA Corporation’s shares (currently trading at $671.01) have posted a disappointing 15.9% loss while the S&P 500 was down 7.7%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
